<dl id="n08170b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08170b">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08170b"> 170(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> W on roofs watch / single combats</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[on the Battle of Clontarf]</font> The Danish women, and the men left to guard the town, crowded the roofs, remaining all day to watch the fight. <small> Emily Lawless, <a name="ELIS" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ELIS"><cite title="source">Ireland (Story of Nations series</cite></a> (192?) 68</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
